Title: The journey
DateModified: '2019-02-21'
DatePublished: '2019-02-21'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-journey-2
SetInCountry: South Africa
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: TOSCHA WILLIAMS
AuthorCountry: South Africa
Text: "The journey is a story of a young lady that lives in South Africa and all her\
  \ life staying in her country she has never travelled anywhere except in her city\
  \ Cape Town. \nShe longed to travel and explore.\nShe is an adventurous person but\
  \ due to her standards of living she was not able to go abroad or even explore her\
  \ country until she was offered a once in a life time opportunity. \nFinally she\
  \ was going to experience the beauty of the world that's surrounding her. \nIt's\
  \ been the thing she was really longing for and now its time. \nHer life then changes\
  \ within her experience of traveling. To be continued....."
